# FriendlyETL

A beginner-friendly and customizable Python ETL (Extract, Transform, Load) package designed for fast and efficient data workflows. Built using Pandas and compatible with files and databases, this package helps you automate your ETL pipelines with just a few lines of code.

## ğŸ”§ Features

- âœ… Extract data from CSV, Excel, JSON, or databases (MySQL)  
- âœ… Clean and transform datasets using common operations  
- âœ… Load data to CSV or back into MySQL databases  
- âœ… Modular and easy to extend for your own workflows  
- âœ… Designed for beginners, students, and professionals alike  

